# Netlify /preview on Apache (same vhost as /monitor, different paths)
#
# Canonical setup lives in this repo:
#   - vps/katago-web-app-port6006.conf — VirtualHost *:6006 with:
#       IncludeOptional /etc/apache2/katago-vhost.d/preview.conf
#   - vps/apache-preview-enable.conf — copy of that optional fragment (Alias
#     /preview-data/…, ProxyPass /preview/ → 127.0.0.1:4173)
#
# Toggle Apache routes (install/remove fragment + graceful reload):
#   sudo ./vps/preview-apache.sh on
#   sudo ./vps/preview-apache.sh off
#   ./vps/preview-apache.sh status
#
# Start/stop the static file server the proxy targets:
#   ./vps/preview-server.sh start
#   ./vps/preview-server.sh stop
#
# Required modules: proxy, proxy_http. Do not point /monitor at :6006 (proxy loop).
# Full /monitor example: see vps/katago-web-app-port6006.conf
